      "job_description": "\"\n\nCompany Description\n\nWe are one of the leading Digital Transformation Company based out of Bengaluru. We have served more than 90 happy clients across the globe with an excellent track record since we started in 2017.\n\nRole Description\n\nThis is a full-time on-site role for a Senior Java Developer located in Bengaluru. The Senior Java Developer will be responsible for designing, implementing, and maintaining Java applications, collaborating with cross-functional teams to develop high-quality software solutions, and ensuring the performance, quality, and responsiveness of applications. The Senior Java Developer will also mentor junior developers, conduct code reviews, and contribute to the continuous improvement of development processes.\n\nQualifications\n• Strong proficiency in Java programming language\n• Experience with Java frameworks such as Spring, springboot, Mangodb and Hibernate\n• Knowledge of software development principles, design patterns, and best practices\n• Experience with relational databases and SQL\n• Experience with web development technologies such as HTML, CSS, and JavaScript\n• Good understanding of agile development methodologies\n• Excellent problem-solving and debugging skills\n• Ability to work effectively in a team environment\n• Bachelor's degree in Computer Science or a related field\n• Minimum of 5 years of experience in Java development\n\n\"",
