      "job_description": "Job Description:\n\nWe are seeking a talented and experienced Senior Java Developer to join our dynamic team. The ideal candidate will have a strong foundation in computer science and a proven track record in software development, particularly in Java and related technologies. If you are passionate about coding, thrive in an agile environment, and have a knack for solving complex problems, we would love to meet you!\n\nResponsibilities:\n• Develop and maintain high-quality Java applications, adhering to best practices and coding standards.\n• Design and implement REST APIs and microservices.\n• Work with Spring Boot and other related frameworks to build scalable applications.\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams to define, design, and ship new features.\n• Troubleshoot and resolve issues along the CI/CD pipeline, ensuring smooth transitions from development to production.\n• Engage in code reviews, source control management, and continuous improvement processes.\n• Communicate effectively with clients to understand their requirements and deliver solutions that exceed expectations.\n\nMust Have:\n• Education: BE, B. Tech, MCA, or higher.\n• Experience: 5-8 years of industry experience in related technologies.\n• Skills: Strong foundation in computer science, including data structures, algorithms, databases, and distributed systems.\n• Proficiency: Expertise in Java software development (minimum Java 8) and Spring Boot.\n• Microservices: Experience in at least one microservice project.\n• Database: General understanding of SQL or NoSQL databases.\n• Cloud: Basic experience with cloud technologies (Azure preferred).\n• Software Engineering: Familiarity with agile methodologies, coding standards, code reviews, source control management, build processes, test automation, and CI/CD pipelines.\n• CI/CD: Experience in moving code from development/test to staging and production.\n• Client Communication: Excellent communication skills for interacting with clients.\n\nShould Have:\n• Understanding of framework design and modeling, and the impact of object model design in a large-scale multi-tenant environment.\n• Proficiency in working with Linux or macOS environments.\n• Basic knowledge of JavaScript front-end UI frameworks (React/Angular), with the ability to perform minimal bug fixes.\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary and benefits package.\n• Opportunities for professional growth and development.\n• A collaborative and inclusive work environment.\n• Cutting-edge projects and the chance to work with the latest technologies.\n\nIf you are a driven and innovative Java Developer looking to take your career to the next level, we encourage you to apply, or send an email to aainas@recruitsy.in",
