      "job_description": "Company Description\n\nVikgol is a software development company located in Bengaluru.\n\nWe provide on-demand software development services, offering access to top-quality teams of developers, designers, and product managers.\n\nWith our streamlined process, users can quickly get a fixed price quote and access a team of top-tier talent.\n\nWe pride ourselves on our high-quality network of engineers, product managers, and designers, and we use automation to increase efficiency and reliability in software development.\n\nRole Description\n\nThis is a full-time on-site role for a Java Developer with 3-8 years of relevant experience at Vikgol in Bengaluru.\n\nAs a Java Developer, you will be responsible for day-to-day tasks related to software development, including building microservices and implementing programming solutions using the Spring Framework and Java.\n\nYou will work closely with our team of developers, designers, and product managers to deliver high-quality software solutions.\n\nQualifications\n• 3-8 years of relevant experience is a must\n• Strong experience in software development, particularly in Java, Python\n• Proficiency in building microservices and understanding of microservices architecture\n• Excellent programming skills\n• Experience with the Spring Framework\n\nAdditional qualifications and skills that would be beneficial for this role include :\n• Experience with agile development practices\n• Knowledge of cloud technologies such as AWS or Azure\n• Familiarity with frontend frameworks like Angular or React\n• Ability to work collaboratively in a team environment\n• Excellent problem-solving and troubleshooting skills\n• Good communication and interpersonal skills\n\nRequired Tech Stack : Java, Python, Docker, AWS/ Azure/ GCP, Microservices.\n\nLocation : Bangalore\n\n(ref:hirist.tech)",
